Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.05,0:00:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(330,400)\fad(1000,000)}圣天空战记
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.43,0:00:12.43,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是只要坠入爱河每个人都会变得如此孤单?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.51,0:00:21.42,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是正拥抱着比黑暗要更深沉的苦楚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.48,0:00:34.56,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一切必定都是为了让我俩能绽放光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.03,0:00:39.47,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爱着你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.53,0:00:43.97,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直用心凝视着你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.04,0:00:48.48,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信着你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.54,0:00:53.04,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便是在寒冷的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.07,0:01:15.50,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在用泪水来呼唤你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.57,0:01:20.03,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不需要约定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.11,0:01:28.91,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你早就给了我 最宝贵的坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.43,0:00:12.43,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ねえ 愛したら誰もが こんな孤独になるの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.51,0:00:21.42,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ねえ 暗闇よりも深い苦しみ 抱きしめてるの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.48,0:00:34.56,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何もかもが二人 輝くためきっと
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.03,0:00:39.47,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君を君を愛してる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.53,0:00:43.97,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心で見つめている
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.04,0:00:48.48,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君を君を信じてる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.54,0:00:53.04,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寒い夜も
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.07,0:01:15.50,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涙で今呼びかける
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.57,0:01:20.03,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約束などいらない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.11,0:01:28.91,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君がくれた大切な強さだから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.49,0:01:33.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快放我们出去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.96,0:01:35.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是什么意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.83,0:01:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然把我们关在这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.23,0:01:39.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.16,0:01:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快把我们放出去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.00,0:01:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.10,0:01:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们给我安分点
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.07,0:01:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臭和尚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.17,0:01:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是寨巴哈打来了,我看你们怎么死
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.54,0:01:52.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直就跟山贼没两样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.51,0:01:54.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最好也给我小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.08,0:01:57.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别在普拉克度大人面前露出本性
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.22,0:02:10.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死的预言
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.60,0:02:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里等着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.98,0:02:32.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好诡异的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.15,0:02:36.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西特王子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.06,0:02:41.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请告诉我你真正的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.26,0:02:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们看起来像是叛国者吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.93,0:02:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们看起来像在撒谎吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.00,0:02:51.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.10,0:02:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过,普拉克度的法术将会道出真相
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.21,0:02:57.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你相信我们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.84,0:03:00.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是这个国家的王子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.91,0:03:04.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦普拉克度有所进言
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.28,0:03:07.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王族就会加以采纳,这是我国的惯例
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.52,0:03:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是为了国家好也是为了人民好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.76,0:03:13.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了国家…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.46,0:03:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来你们都是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.83,0:03:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵跟你都是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.13,0:03:20.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.37,0:03:25.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问话的时间到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.71,0:03:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要从小瞳开始审问?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.77,0:03:30.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一切都与她无关
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.14,0:03:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你们没做坏事由谁开始审问不都一样吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.05,0:03:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在搞这些事的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.52,0:03:39.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寨巴哈的那些家伙会…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.35,0:03:45.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波利斯大人,希望你能相信我们是为了传达真相而来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.36,0:03:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们真的明白自己目前的处境吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.43,0:03:53.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.90,0:03:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才阿斯多利亚王国,派了使者前来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.50,0:04:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说贵国正在悬赏你们的人头及艾斯嘉科尼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.38,0:04:07.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.58,0:04:10.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连他不是会说谎的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.38,0:04:12.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你相信我们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.75,0:04:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.95,0:04:16.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真相只有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.79,0:04:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等到普拉克度的审问结束,一切真相就会大白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.73,0:04:30.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球…那是你国家的名称吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.84,0:04:31.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.27,0:04:34.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个国家位于何方?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.11,0:04:36.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空的另一方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.14,0:04:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻之月
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.24,0:04:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻之月?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.55,0:04:44.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是从幻之月来的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.52,0:04:46.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.89,0:04:48.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那个遭受诅咒之地来的?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.05,0:04:49.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.42,0:04:52.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.79,0:04:57.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说你们偷袭了寨巴哈的浮游要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.70,0:05:01.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还破坏了能源石的矿山
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.47,0:05:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.84,0:05:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?快回答我!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.54,0:05:10.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答案究竟为何?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.78,0:05:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.91,0:05:17.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说的与阿斯多利亚所转述的罪状一致
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.18,0:05:19.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.25,0:05:20.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问问她理由
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.22,0:05:23.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这当然就是为了要篡夺阿斯多利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.76,0:05:25.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俘虏也已经证实了这点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.33,0:05:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是怎么晓得浮游要塞与矿山的位置?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.57,0:05:37.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,探测术…靠这个坠子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.94,0:05:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,探测术?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.77,0:05:42.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用内心看见…看不到的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.18,0:05:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是那股不可思议的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.84,0:05:49.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是用那种力量看到了隐形的人型装甲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.51,0:05:50.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.68,0:05:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩,把那条项链交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.78,0:06:17.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是什么地方?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.05,0:06:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这混帐对我做了什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.38,0:06:26.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那才是你…真正的模样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.65,0:06:29.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法术解除了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.66,0:06:31.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你做的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.59,0:06:34.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.96,0:06:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波利斯,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.06,0:06:38.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不晓得
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.30,0:06:46.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人,快放我出去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.81,0:06:52.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.45,0:07:02.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.52,0:07:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候的情景为什么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.36,0:07:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是杀人凶手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.16,0:07:10.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是幻人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.63,0:07:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拥有多种脸孔,但却没有自己的脸孔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.83,0:07:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生于战争也死于战争
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.70,0:07:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长老…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.21,0:07:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我族遭诅咒的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.76,0:07:44.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄…兄长
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.07,0:07:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄…兄长
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.64,0:07:53.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怨恨这个世界吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.01,0:07:55.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怨恨自己的命运吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.61,0:08:01.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那一出生即见不得天日\N只能在战争中求生存的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.28,0:08:05.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宗基啊,跟我来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.62,0:08:10.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解放缠着你们的命运之轮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.56,0:08:14.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗肯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.26,0:08:21.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是你的力量?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.30,0:08:24.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.57,0:08:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然被你知道这么多事,那我就不能留你活□了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.01,0:08:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这是?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.01,0:08:36.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的生命之火即将熄灭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.38,0:08:38.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.89,0:08:42.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是接下来将要发生的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.12,0:08:44.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.03,0:08:50.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说我会死吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.60,0:08:55.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.93,0:08:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.40,0:08:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.47,0:08:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.35,0:09:09.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.42,0:09:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太可怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.75,0:09:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个女孩太可怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.42,0:09:18.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.62,0:09:19.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.73,0:09:22.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了?普拉克度大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.86,0:09:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么,只是有点累
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.60,0:09:26.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的瞳孔放大了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.00,0:09:29.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姨,她的情况如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.30,0:09:33.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心脏…停止了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.94,0:09:40.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生了什么事?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.68,0:09:43.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那声惨叫是怎么回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.92,0:09:44.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俘虏死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.22,0:09:48.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的同伴死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.69,0:09:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.69,0:09:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.69,0:09:52.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.59,0:09:55.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳她…小瞳她…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.99,0:09:57.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王子,求求您
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.16,0:09:58.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快放我们出去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.76,0:09:59.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.03,0:10:01.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托您快放了我们,王子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.77,0:10:03.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西特
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.91,0:10:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.07,0:10:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.48,0:10:11.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们这些混帐…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.48,0:10:13.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把门打开
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.81,0:10:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.08,0:10:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作点,振作点啊,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.16,0:10:34.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然敢做出这种事\N我们绝对不会轻易饶了你们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.87,0:10:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦请把路让出来吧,波利斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.88,0:10:51.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.38,0:10:53.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.25,0:10:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂,你振作点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.72,0:10:58.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行,还是没反应
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.93,0:11:01.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样子做,对吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.09,0:11:03.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.76,0:11:04.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,配合
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.80,0:11:06.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,配合你自己的心跳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.90,0:11:07.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,配合心跳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.07,0:11:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.91,0:11:17.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再用力一点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.38,0:11:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用力点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.64,0:11:20.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别死
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.71,0:11:21.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别死啊,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.41,0:11:23.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.80,0:11:46.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.51,0:11:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你别死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.77,0:11:50.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳,快醒过来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.05,0:11:55.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.92,0:12:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒醒啊,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.13,0:12:10.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.77,0:12:15.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她复活了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.80,0:12:18.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.27,0:12:22.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还活着,你还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.44,0:12:25.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露露
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.51,0:12:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的磨爪刀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.22,0:12:31.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙给我站起来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.18,0:12:34.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.02,0:12:38.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳,你怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.83,0:12:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冒牌货…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.66,0:12:44.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人…会死
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.03,0:12:45.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.40,0:12:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冒牌货…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.93,0:12:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人…会死
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.64,0:12:51.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.81,0:13:04.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她竟然…竟然说我会死?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.42,0:13:13.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不会受到幻觉影响
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.19,0:13:18.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得快点去通知弗肯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.57,0:13:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普拉克度是赛巴哈的间谋?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.17,0:13:27.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.04,0:13:31.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人杀了真正的普拉克度
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.28,0:13:32.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改变外貌
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.94,0:13:34.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还杀了那名俘虏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.18,0:13:38.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那个人也会被黑色的手给…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.45,0:13:41.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普拉克度人在哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.85,0:13:43.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四处都不见他的踪影
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.62,0:13:44.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一定是溜了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.22,0:13:47.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西特王子,得快去追他才行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.29,0:13:51.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再拖下去的话,小瞳的秘密就会被寨巴哈得知
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.06,0:13:52.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.26,0:13:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.27,0:13:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您不能相信这些家伙的胡言乱语
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.40,0:13:58.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.66,0:14:21.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西特
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.36,0:14:25.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.23,0:14:29.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信他人这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.47,0:14:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时会比上战场,还需要更多的勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.88,0:14:40.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.55,0:14:43.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.58,0:14:46.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你能亲自将寨巴哈的间谋找出来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.29,0:14:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.35,0:14:49.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您是认真的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.46,0:14:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己的清白就由自己来证明
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.32,0:14:56.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要让他们也遵照弗雷特公国的法规行事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.16,0:14:58.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,责任由我来担
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.73,0:15:01.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.57,0:15:03.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.70,0:15:07.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的伤势尚未痊愈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.91,0:15:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我代替他去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.14,0:15:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.15,0:15:20.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管那个人是怎样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.99,0:15:22.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不能让那种的预知成真
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.16,0:15:26.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了吗?小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.20,0:15:32.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边有座塔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.16,0:15:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.57,0:15:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们不会趁机逃走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.17,0:15:44.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.01,0:15:48.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连对梵的信赖
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.19,0:15:57.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是幻之月的人?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.46,0:15:58.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.62,0:16:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她能够见到隐形之物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.53,0:16:02.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有能力知道过去与未来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.83,0:16:05.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是名令人畏惧的女子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.26,0:16:08.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够见到隐形之物并且知道未来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.30,0:16:11.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.87,0:16:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.51,0:16:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.11,0:16:24.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.22,0:16:31.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个女的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.69,0:16:35.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害我受了这个伤
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.20,0:16:39.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得好,宗基
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.26,0:16:41.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢您的夸奖
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.10,0:16:47.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是奖赏,你就收下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.67,0:16:50.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您这是要做什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.01,0:16:53.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你杀了米盖尔,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.08,0:16:55.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那是任务…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.28,0:16:58.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟然敢那样对待我的部下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.48,0:17:01.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样我才讨厌幻人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.22,0:17:03.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.46,0:17:10.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那个吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.56,0:17:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵,再快一点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.13,0:17:16.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪兰度…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.91,0:17:22.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会来不及的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.84,0:17:27.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.41,0:17:29.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.85,0:17:33.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗肯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.22,0:17:36.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.56,0:17:43.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.00,0:17:46.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾斯嘉科尼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.66,0:17:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是走运
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.77,0:17:49.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歇士达,迦迪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.50,0:17:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳,振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.68,0:18:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是那些隐形的家伙吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.15,0:18:08.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.82,0:18:10.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,专心…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.49,0:18:12.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,专心地想着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.59,0:18:14.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在心中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.73,0:18:17.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个时候怎么可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.20,0:18:21.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定…一定办得到的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.31,0:18:32.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来啊,来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.61,0:18:33.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点下来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.32,0:18:43.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集中精神,专心地想像…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.43,0:18:54.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.27,0:18:57.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.91,0:19:04.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这混帐…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.62,0:19:15.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.05,0:19:17.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻之月来的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.06,0:19:21.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪兰度大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.83,0:19:29.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.27,0:19:35.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臭女人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.48,0:19:40.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的目标是小瞳?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.75,0:19:46.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.52,0:19:49.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是你在坏我好事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.57,0:20:02.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想逃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.84,0:20:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胆小鬼!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.61,0:20:16.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟小瞳的预言一样?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.21,0:20:21.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在已经没有证据能证明那个\N普拉克度是寨巴哈的间谋了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.35,0:20:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.79,0:20:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们已经证实各位的清白了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.59,0:20:31.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正牌普拉克度的遗体已经被人发现了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.23,0:20:34.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是修行僧在森林里发现的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.43,0:20:39.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被吸干的遗体,确实为幻人所为
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.87,0:20:42.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算没有证据我也相信你们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.91,0:20:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你们肯再回来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.78,0:20:48.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.11,0:20:52.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请原谅我之前诸多无礼之处
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.28,0:20:54.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你让西特下定决心的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.35,0:20:58.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们长得好像喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.32,0:21:01.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论是眼睛还是头发的颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.19,0:21:04.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直就像是兄弟一样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.84,0:21:12.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.97,0:21:14.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公王已经归来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.47,0:21:16.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父王回来了?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.32,0:21:37.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西特的父亲会是怎么样的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.11,0:22:57.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西特王子,我来帮你占卜一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.48,0:23:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禁忌之恋?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.92,0:23:08.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘密之扉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.08,0:21:58.15,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月儿彼方蓝色探照灯照耀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.69,0:22:06.60,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然降临的天使 你究竟是谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.06,0:22:14.23,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命运的门扉即将开启　So just fall in love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.54,0:22:20.38,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝不放过这令人兴奋的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.45,0:22:22.74,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stop,baby
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.98,0:22:27.75,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那燃烧般的神秘双眸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.82,0:22:31.59,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天真无邪的笑容让我倾倒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.66,0:22:35.39,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞳眸深处的暗示只传递给你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.46,0:22:39.40,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始了无止尽的旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.46,0:22:42.90,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内心的鼓动无法抑制
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.96,0:22:50.37,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想带着你一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.08,0:21:58.14,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月の向こう　蒼い Search light　重なる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.69,0:22:06.59,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然舞い降りたAngel　そう　君は誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.06,0:22:14.23,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今　運命の　扉が開く　So just fall in love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.54,0:22:20.37,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸騒ぎするこの瞬間を逃がさない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.44,0:22:22.74,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stop,baby
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.98,0:22:27.75,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,焼けそうな　君の Mystic eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.82,0:22:31.58,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無邪気な笑顔で　Breaking down
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.65,0:22:35.38,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君だけに　瞳の奥の合図
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.46,0:22:39.39,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果てない　旅は始まる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.46,0:22:42.90,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,もう止まらない　胸の鼓動
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.96,0:22:50.37,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君を　さらっていきたい


